{"tid":1554842,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"香港過欄challenge ！！！","createTime":"2019-09-09T06:37:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T09:59:20.000Z","uid":90004,"like":119,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"20908baf79e78a71fc585777b41fded60c312092","tid":1554842,"uid":90004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:37:21.000Z","msg":"唔知有無手足同我有同一樣嘅諗法<br />\n香港人成日都唔做運動，身體好差，成日病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，不如整依個有益身心嘅活動，一齊練下過欄<br />\n拍段片放上 哎豬 比人睇下你練習嘅成果再tag人，威威比人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n難度無所謂，揀一兩個練，練順佢，只係想大家過得熟手姐<br />\n<br />\n9月10日 8pm 開始 po 片威威比人睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返：最後孭埋個袋練啦，你地成日都會帶袋出街架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n教學片段：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F3f1NhFzW9w&amp;list=LLBHOazJxCAmXlj7Cayui2Tw&amp;index=2&amp;t=54s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DF3f1NhFzW9w%26list%3DLLBHOazJxCAmXlj7Cayui2Tw%26index%3D2%26t%3D54s&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kYL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=b976889d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F3f1NhFzW9w&amp;list=LLBHOazJxCAmXlj7Cayui2Tw&amp;index=2&amp;t=54s</a>"},{"pid":"72fdcb0506cb8c485c986ca81a9e55c53372676d","tid":1554842,"uid":90004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c3ff8a7f6a50b920a703ee87d7711b1a365692c","tid":1554842,"uid":90004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:38:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\